{
  "stem": "422.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I survived the ghetto because I was working at a place that was for them very important.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The soldiers were on the Stalingrad, in Russia, fighting the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed-- there were a lot of cold there, a lot of frost, a lot of snow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They needed those furs, and I was working on this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the ship-- ship coats for the soldiers, that kept them warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A matter of fact, I was two times taken away from the machine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was an operator.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they decided that women are not needed no more, women are not productive enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was taken away from the machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they want to send me away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I looked around, and I stayed with old women, little kids, which I knew right away where I am going.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the manager of that division went over to that SS man, pointed at me-- this was two times-- that I am very fast.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Without me he can close up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There won't be any work done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I am faster as-- as the men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put me back to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Two times this happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I managed even in Birkenau, in Auschwitz to escape a couple times to hide myself in the lavatory, to hide myself from selections.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Matter of fact, they took us once from the barrack where we were working, in Birkenau, to the sauna to give blood.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had the nerve to take Jewish blood for their wounded soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I said, I would rather die, and I won't give them my blood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I jumped out onto the SS man's back, from a high, you know, from a window.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a ground, but was high.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
